UCB in 150 mln Bfr Chinese joint venture . Belgian pharmaceuticals and chemicals firm UCB said on Friday it had signed an agreement with Chinese group SBC to set up a joint venture in Shanghai for the production of choline chloride . The investment in the joint venture - expected to have an annual turnover of about 500 million Belgian francs - would be 150 million francs , UCB said in a statement . The plant would have capacity of 12 , 000 tonnes a year and employ 40 people . 
